<div class="row">

  <div class="small-12 large-6 columns">

    <h3>Candidates</h3>
    <div>
      <h6>What is the application process like?</h6>
      <p>We encourage EVERYONE who needs finanical aid to apply, although unfortunately only a select number of students will be selected for the scholarships.</p>
        <ol>
          <li>The first step is to sign up and complete the application.</li>
          <li>After submitting the application, we will review your application for approval.</li>
          <li>If approved, your profile will be posted to our website. Donors will read the profiles and nominate the one that they find most compelling.</li>
          <li>If nominated for a campaign, we will contact you as to when it will be held and steps on how to publicize it your community!</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h6>Who can apply?</h6>
      <p>Anyone with financial needs! Please note that our primary focus is to help those with the most need and barriers to joining the tech community. Additionally, all candidates will be properly vetted by our selection committee to ensure the financial need and user stories are accurate.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h6>Do I need to have been accepted to a development bootcamp already to apply?</h6>
      <p>No, you do not need to be accepted already. After a candidate has been selected for our upcoming campaign, the candidate should apply to Dev Bootcamp.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h6>If I am already accepted, am I able to apply for a scholarship?</h6>
      <p>Yes, but please realize that if approved, the campaign will occur in the future and therefore we cannot advance the tuition. The tuition can only be paid after the fundraising goal has been achieved.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h6>What happens if as the candidate, I do not achieve my fundraising goal?</h6>
      <p>If the fundraising goal is not achieved during the campaign, we will still stand by you. We are investing in you as a person for your success. We will strategize with our mentors to see if we can help you raise the additional funding for tuition.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h6>If I am not selected for a campaign, what happens next?</h6>
      <p>Although we wish we could fund everyone, unfortunately this is not possible. However, our community of supporters are a great resource and we can try and connect you with a mentor for both tech questions, advice for getting involved in our community and advice on how to raise funds to go to Dev Bootcamp!</p>
    </div>

  </div>


</div>
